{"tid":1611952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對峙不如伏擊 引狗入窮巷獅鳥啦","createTime":"2019-10-02T05:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:39:36.000Z","uid":28759,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0cfbd6d7407b923f5d736cf242561710c6665554","tid":1611952,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:58:56.000Z","msg":"依家啲狗情緒失控<br />\n引幾隻狗落單追人唔難<br />\n只要挑釁 Lv 1 都叫得郁<br />\n三四隻狗追撚到入後巷都夠膽<br />\n入到後巷又窄又冇 CAM<br />\n有準備少少淋鋤水都贏<br />\n<br />\n事前準備<br />\n有學「挑釁」技能嘅敏捷遊俠<br />\n後巷一條，區區都有<br />\n後巷準備啲咩都得<br />\n陷阱流道具流<br />\n<br />\n唔會搞到居民<br />\n又可以由最撚惡嗰幾隻打起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n確保冇 CAM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落單追市民追得咁撚爽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac0fb142afcf5bd588e96ddbd61e35e02eb3b31","tid":1611952,"uid":104758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:59:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf814a64426f41b7b8c4f3210f3afd9ac13935e","tid":1611952,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:00:21.000Z","msg":"都on9<br />\n怕你偷雞唔成食咋米炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c800ca9c883a4b3b3dfa40a49d0e5efb16119e5","tid":1611952,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"接仔放工最實際。"},{"pid":"4e1a3c2426f7214719a6a27f9d450b57e90a0b57","tid":1611952,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:02:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"627359802e163fac78e901e0ce87cb1e63a78dc6","tid":1611952,"uid":51057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:08:15.000Z","msg":"入後巷...失手比人捉到就仆街..."},{"pid":"6ade7234dc26e58f0d4097aef80d326204242e40","tid":1611952,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10